{"tid":1382520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日發夢我見到一幕好感人既畫面（香港的非華裔）","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:36:05.000Z","uid":228962,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ecec0506f513cfa48381a057893609077e5609e","tid":1382520,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:27:36.000Z","msg":"話說琴日發夢果陣 我看到有為數不少既南亞裔人士或其他在港少數族裔都有做人鏈 做後排 見到真系好感動<br />\n你地可能一直係香港都會受人不重視又或者被歧視 但到香港有事既時候 你地都會願意站出黎 真係好感動 我好希望大家香港人都可以改變對在港非華裔既一些偏見 <br />\n<br />\n所以我想同一班同樣愛香港愛自由既在港非華裔少數民族講聲<br />\n<br />\n多謝你地 你地都係香港人！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172161fe837ed580760aad52f12ef2197fe607d5","tid":1382520,"uid":276716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eN9vUjA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeN9vUjA.jpg&h=f6fbd8e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6f57815f22bb220e7d313eb6b3ac6f9a39fc1ea","tid":1382520,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"推 真係好想多謝返一班香港既少數族裔 就算佢地有付出過 都可能無咩人提及佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211498d124d97edb8ffcf23e1097a9b58a1f4722","tid":1382520,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:32:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef63c4d2427a9afc4fb9688b3fed45f3e04093ed","tid":1382520,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"錯怪左南亞仔"},{"pid":"ddabbd3e08d3090fd0115060c9f4c15d9ecc7848","tid":1382520,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"琴日琴夢我見到佢地仲要咩裝備都無 都係度幫手"},{"pid":"5ba8013faa16b0f2640c01f551520804d65b172b","tid":1382520,"uid":228962,"like":0,"dislike